Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.49,0:06:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個集滿100張就能拿到贈品呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.04,0:06:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一百張
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.62,0:06:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能拿到什麼來著
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.32,0:06:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獎牌哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.52,0:06:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,商店街的獎牌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.57,0:06:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我也沒有見過  聽說是有兔子在搗年糕的圖案
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.81,0:06:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易集了這麼多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.18,0:06:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總算  總算是集夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.84,0:06:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是獎牌紀念日
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.18,0:06:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.53,0:06:46.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請注意安全
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.98,0:06:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要連蒂拉也這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.96,0:06:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.01,0:06:55.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才怎麼感覺好像有什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.20,0:06:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,餅藏？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.62,0:07:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小  小玉  成了遙遠  國度的  王  王妃大…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.15,0:07:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不是什麼王妃大人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.48,0:07:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  說的也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.84,0:07:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也說不准真是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.22,0:07:12.14,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大餅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.94,0:07:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了對了  看看這個  只差三個章就集滿一百張了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.30,0:07:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來看啊看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.93,0:07:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧是吧  了不起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.62,0:07:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.58,0:07:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  集的好辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.23,0:07:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是說  小玉要和王子結婚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.78,0:07:32.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嫁入豪門啊  不愧是小玉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.95,0:07:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們怎麼就相信了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.33,0:07:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想想小玉的樣兒  不可能是真的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.55,0:07:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  也不會連個預兆都沒有就突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.66,0:07:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.97,0:07:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什麼時候來的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.07,0:07:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.03,0:07:46.32,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女忍者小玉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.15,0:07:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王妃的事怎麼說？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.31,0:07:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小喬伊誤會了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.32,0:07:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可太可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.63,0:07:55.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是沒準真的能成為王妃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.89,0:07:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史織你這是狗嘴裡能吐出象牙論
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.63,0:08:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小玉  不是我信不過小喬伊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.21,0:08:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你最好留個心眼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.93,0:08:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小綠則是陰謀論嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.22,0:08:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便一提我是生意興隆論
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.01,0:08:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把小玉挖走  讓她在年糕難吃氏家族裡生產年糕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.54,0:08:16.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後打造出小島名產之年糕！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.98,0:08:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小喬伊你真是個了不起的軍師
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.14,0:08:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會啦不會啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.85,0:08:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.62,0:08:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.65,0:08:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喬伊大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.59,0:08:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說少女就是王妃  我怎麼也不能…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.82,0:08:33.65,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還一次都沒有再占卜…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.06,0:08:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  來  蒂拉  今天得把你的通信功能修好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.02,0:08:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.77,0:08:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總算收到祖國那邊寄來的修理方法了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.50,0:08:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.95,0:08:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.83,0:08:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.65,0:08:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接找小喬伊去問個清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.87,0:08:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.92,0:08:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王子大人就是我們上次看到的那個人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.40,0:08:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.58,0:09:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來上次小蒂拉有投影出來過什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.09,0:09:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小史織你意外地八卦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.29,0:09:05.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.07,0:09:07.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  大家聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.58,0:09:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  小玉  抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.59,0:09:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊  差不多積夠商店街的積分卡了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.49,0:09:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我邊買晚飯的東西邊回去好不
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.89,0:09:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當了個然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.67,0:09:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  歡迎光臨王妃大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.92,0:09:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王妃大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.53,0:09:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一下變成VIP了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.44,0:09:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  不要這樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.14,0:09:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩塊木棉豆腐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.53,0:09:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.48,0:09:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有這個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.96,0:09:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.09,0:09:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.46,0:09:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.56,0:09:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  太好了  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.89,0:09:56.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  我先回家把之前的卡拿來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.28,0:09:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家能不能在兔湯等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.87,0:09:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.92,0:10:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.84,0:10:02.55,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是貼在這種地方的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.85,0:10:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玉子大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.62,0:10:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小喬伊我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.97,0:10:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玉子大…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.32,0:10:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉小喬伊  我去去就來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.73,0:10:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少女喲  你又發什麼瘋了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.82,0:10:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒂拉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.53,0:10:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您又有什麼重要事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.23,0:10:29.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少女喲  正常應該是被選作王妃更讓你開心才對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.08,0:10:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  但是那事讓人覺得太過意外了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.64,0:10:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個金牌是我用章換來的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.04,0:10:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從小學開始就一點一點地集了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.84,0:10:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說  這個更讓我開心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.04,0:10:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小玉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.73,0:10:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總算成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.96,0:10:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.79,0:10:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說商店街只有我一個人有這個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.78,0:10:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虧你能集那麼多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.12,0:10:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.61,0:10:55.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玉子大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.90,0:10:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您繁忙時打擾非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.25,0:11:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  豆大
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.01,0:11:10.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.85,0:11:11.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喬伊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.67,0:11:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到你健康比什麼都好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.30,0:11:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  這傢伙是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.80,0:11:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位就是曾在信中提到的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.65,0:11:19.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玉子北白川
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.26,0:11:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  你好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.50,0:11:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玉子北白川
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.45,0:11:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是倒著說個全名而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.98,0:11:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.77,0:11:29.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他用的這柱子很讚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.67,0:11:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.96,0:11:32.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫  梅查·年糕難吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.96,0:11:32.22,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音同超級  年糕難吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.76,0:11:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說啥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.80,0:11:35.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豆大  冷靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.61,0:11:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法嘛  人家就叫這個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.80,0:11:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都有血緣關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.93,0:11:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和蒂拉雖然同享王室的姓氏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.13,0:11:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但並不是親戚關係
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.12,0:11:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侍奉王室的人都能享有同一姓氏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.80,0:11:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玉子大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.86,0:11:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喬伊和蒂拉給你添了不少麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.00,0:11:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忠心表示感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.20,0:11:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡哪裡  不必客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.73,0:12:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  我一直想要對你道謝…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.08,0:12:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狀態還不是太好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.34,0:12:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣啊  喬伊大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.02,0:12:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少讓玉子大人和王子大人互相打了招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.97,0:12:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是本大人出馬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.66,0:12:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,效果拔群啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.05,0:12:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般的手機還比這個信號好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.17,0:12:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是個很溫和的王子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.17,0:12:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是個很優秀的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.31,0:12:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開朗  聰明
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.04,0:12:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時又十分謙虛  受到全國人民的愛戴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.89,0:12:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但看上去還是個孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.89,0:12:35.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實還很年輕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.62,0:12:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過很稱職
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.30,0:12:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是說了兩句話還判斷不出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.86,0:12:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,餅藏  你對喬伊這麼說也沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.80,0:12:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  小喬伊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.44,0:12:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我果然還是覺得我並不是王妃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.10,0:12:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驚動大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.61,0:12:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.66,0:13:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小玉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.54,0:13:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.52,0:13:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喬伊大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.80,0:13:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不也挺好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.15,0:13:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王子大人  挺美妙的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.68,0:13:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想親眼現場看看那個柱子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.99,0:13:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很在意它的構造
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.12,0:13:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.45,0:13:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.45,0:13:22.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼能這樣毫不在意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.21,0:13:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然發生這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.25,0:13:25.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼突然
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.40,0:13:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要做比喻的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.94,0:13:31.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像我的毛熊玩具被沒收了一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.65,0:13:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.06,0:13:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我理解  有點害怕對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.50,0:13:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺有什麼突然改變了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.05,0:13:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小綠
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.22,0:13:51.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也感覺好像就要進入宇宙一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.73,0:13:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心裡沒底
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.77,0:13:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  最害怕的一定是小玉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.88,0:14:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.40,0:14:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是王子大人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.74,0:14:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫姐姐玉子大人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.01,0:14:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇了我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.50,0:14:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.88,0:14:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後小玉怎麼著了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.94,0:14:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.18,0:14:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天吃豆腐漢堡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.30,0:14:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玉子大人  換我來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.69,0:14:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  小喬伊  一起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.67,0:14:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.44,0:14:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小喬伊  能幫我攪一下這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.64,0:14:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.84,0:14:31.60,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接用手就行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.47,0:14:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.93,0:14:36.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都與王子打過照面了  差不多要面對現實了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.49,0:14:39.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒂拉  下來  太沒禮貌了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.77,0:14:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.82,0:14:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊  已經不能再站在少女頭上了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.82,0:14:48.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  我出去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.63,0:14:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.01,0:14:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兔子湯有集會
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.62,0:14:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  今天有集會嗎  晚飯怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.86,0:14:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃烏龍麵去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.66,0:15:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  這可是爸爸最喜歡的豆腐漢堡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.96,0:15:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰說我喜歡那玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.81,0:15:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做了我沒辦法就湊和吃罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.44,0:15:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好過分  你要這樣我就真嫁出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.85,0:15:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你等等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.46,0:15:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.37,0:15:19.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去集會
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.12,0:15:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  要嫁出去那是氣話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.05,0:15:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.76,0:15:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.45,0:15:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒂拉的祖國在這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.26,0:15:34.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是個不錯的國家哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.64,0:15:36.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  my Junior
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.38,0:15:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人平靜不下來  對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.93,0:15:40.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才  才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.25,0:15:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您怎麼想  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.10,0:15:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.02,0:15:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別那麼生氣嘛  父親大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.33,0:15:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺像是童話一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.64,0:15:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小百合你回來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.68,0:15:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心不下小玉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.14,0:16:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得去沏茶了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.49,0:16:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝了  麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.38,0:16:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個  對於小玉可能是件好事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.05,0:16:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希望小玉能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.88,0:16:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸福啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.57,0:16:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是還太年輕了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.48,0:16:16.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和小綠一個年紀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.37,0:16:19.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  這事也得參考小玉的意見吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.58,0:16:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不相信小玉是什麼王妃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.70,0:16:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豆大  雖然小玉可能不是王妃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.76,0:16:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過有一天小玉想嫁人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.20,0:16:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得笑著送她走才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.64,0:16:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小玉  不管是店裡的事還是家裡的事  都做的很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.11,0:16:45.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是總不能一直把小玉栓在這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.22,0:16:49.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小玉可能說不想離開這條商店街
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.21,0:16:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.12,0:16:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果小玉可以得到幸福的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.94,0:16:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們不要在這裡瞎插嘴了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.12,0:17:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小玉啊  小玉是我的女兒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.52,0:17:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是  一點都不考慮我的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.08,0:17:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豆大曾喜歡的曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.44,0:17:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為雛子所作曲子的藍本
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.60,0:17:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時候  有失才有所得
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.64,0:17:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐擁手中的一切 可能並不是幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.17,0:17:49.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是酒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.95,0:17:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我試著做了下愛爾蘭咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.95,0:17:52.89,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\alpha&HFF}aaaaaaaaaaaa{\alpha}Irish Coffee
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.41,0:17:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少女  來杯水
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.29,0:17:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.10,0:18:04.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸還沒回來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.28,0:18:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.12,0:18:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時候  也想自己一個人待一會兒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.60,0:18:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.13,0:18:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.10,0:18:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.30,0:18:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  剛才對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.66,0:18:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小玉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.57,0:18:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鱈魚卵？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.72,0:18:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.18,0:18:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小玉  你要  幸福啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.52,0:18:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雞蛋  你要  快變成雞啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.45,0:18:46.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起來起來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.20,0:18:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要睡回房間睡去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.86,0:18:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡多冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.81,0:19:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小玉  我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.25,0:19:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管小玉去哪裡  和誰在一起  只要小玉幸福就好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.74,0:19:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是我  商店街的人都是這麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.65,0:19:15.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣  晚安  請講
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.86,0:19:18.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.50,0:19:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛  大家是想怎樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.15,0:19:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼希望趕我走嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.71,0:19:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你們都搗成年糕算了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.60,0:19:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小玉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.75,0:19:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,餡兒  抱歉  吵醒你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.62,0:19:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒  偶爾也一起睡一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.14,0:19:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小玉也轉過去  我要做小無尾熊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.78,0:20:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.12,0:20:12.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改變  抑或期待  抑或恐懼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.05,0:20:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人心總是矛盾交織
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.09,0:20:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懷揣糾結的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.65,0:20:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧  明天也會依舊到來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.76,0:20:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把獎牌擺在這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.28,0:20:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不見了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.49,0:20:56.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小玉怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.63,0:20:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獎牌不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.30,0:20:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了小玉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.43,0:21:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.34,0:21:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.93,0:21:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獎牌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.92,0:21:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.51,0:21:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了一大早的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.77,0:21:07.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候發現不見的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.07,0:21:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拿到獎牌之後拿給大家看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.51,0:21:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後放到包包裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.80,0:21:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上起來突然想起  一翻包  就不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.88,0:21:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家裡找過了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.06,0:21:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都找遍了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.14,0:21:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找得夠仔細嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.62,0:21:21.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠仔細
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.16,0:21:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰哥哥~
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.48,0:21:25.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰叫你拿著它到處招搖
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.67,0:21:26.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒂拉！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.95,0:21:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為您拿著它各處巡視
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.76,0:21:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是在家裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.59,0:21:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把我的積分卡讓給你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.97,0:21:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有50張呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.93,0:21:38.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  不過不是自己集的沒有意義啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.51,0:21:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的獎牌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.81,0:21:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您找的是這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.93,0:21:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獎牌！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.96,0:23:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眨眼又是一年了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.93,0:23:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是小玉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.00,0:23:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了年末搗年糕的人也變多了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.77,0:23:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年糕的軟硬可以通過手上沾水的多少來調整
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.93,0:23:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家要多多吃年糕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.44,0:23:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以上  我是小玉！
